913. Association between GLP1 Receptor Gene Poly-
morphisms and Reward Learning across Psychiatric
Diagnoses
Hale Yapici Eser1, Candan Yasemin Eren2,
Mehmet Gönen2, Hande Kandemir1, Dilek Yazıcı1, Chia-
Yen Chen3, Dost Ongur4, Diego Pizzagalli4, and Mei-
Hua Hall4
1Koç University School of Medicine,
2Koç University
GSSH,
